Revolver
========

Manage a short list of revolving tasks.
When the last task in the list is done, the next item to-do is the first in the list.

ie....

- workout schedule
- chores
- rotating duties between people
- etc, etc..

Commands
========

revolver input < someinput
- feed it a \n delimited list of things
- reset the current item to the top of the list

revolver next
- find out what's next on the list

revolver done
- mark the current item as done and move on to the next

revolver list
- list all the items

revolver update n
- where n is an index in the list, mark n as the next item
